snippet: Hee Young Park, who shot a career-best 61, moved into the lead as her 20-under-par 193 total left her one shot up on Angela Stanford.
abstract: Hee Young Park takes third-round lead at Manulife Financial LPGA Classic in Waterloo, Ontario.

headline.main: Park Leads at Manulife Financial L.P.G.A. Classic After Shooting a 61
